1. *Avionu* je uklonjen s letačke piste. (The plane was removed from the runway.)
2. On je odlučio da leti *avionom*. (He decided to fly by plane.)
3. Oni su se oprostili od oca pre nego što je on otišao u *avionu*. (They said goodbye to their father before he left by plane.)
4. Oni su ušli u *avion*. (They got on the plane.)
5. Pilot je pogledao u pokazivači tokom leta *avionom*. (The pilot looked at the instruments during the flight of the plane.)